description: The Centers for Medicare and Medicaid Services (CMS) has condensed all 56 Physician Fee Schedule (PFS) carrier specific pricing files into one zip file. It is labeled as All States in the State field, and 2009 in the Calendar Year field. Because the list is ordered by State name, All States appears after the Alaska files. If you sort by most recent Calendar Year, the file will appear at the top of the list.
keyword: Publically Available Data File - for download
title: Physician Fee Schedule Carrier Specific Files
